author: Samsung
description:
Hangeul Truck—where technology meets art and connects the world. At Samsung Galaxy, we believe technology is most meaningful when used to bring people together. In celebration of Hangeul Day, the Hangeul Truck Project brought our philosophy of Openness to six university campuses. Students used Galaxy AI to translate their messages in real time, breaking down language barriers as their words were transformed into a traveling mosaic of Hangeul art.
